{"tid":182470,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)懷念哥哥 英雄本色1-2 縱橫四海","createTime":"2017-04-01T11:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T16:13:41.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9508d55b5a55d515f32e2da4ce87f02ad282418a","tid":182470,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:15:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSergCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=b88be376\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> 關左ADBLOCK可以睇到V台好似係 按左下可轉CC台<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSergCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=2eb4aeef\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/f90274/c0f97e10a1603dba9eb802101a0c75b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Ff90274%2Fc0f97e10a1603dba9eb802101a0c75b4.jpg&h=8804758c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/95/Once_a_Thief.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F95%2FOnce_a_Thief.jpg&h=84e8bc8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.宋子豪（狄龍飾）和李馬克（人稱Mark哥，周潤發飾）是一個國際造偽鈔集團的重要人物，彼此情如手足。子豪的弟弟宋子傑（張國榮飾）受訓於警察學校，女友鍾柔（朱寶意飾）與他情投意合。一次，子豪與Mark到台灣去交易，遭手下譚成（李子雄飾）出賣，自首後入獄。為使子豪不泄密，台灣黑幫來綁架宋父，在打鬥中，宋父喪生。接著Mark為子豪報仇時中槍變成跛子，從此在幫會地位一落千丈，並且被通緝..<br />\n<br />\n2.警方懷疑宋子豪（狄龍飾）的恩師龍四（石天飾）利用船廠做掩護，暗中操縱偽鈔集團，派宋子傑（張國榮飾）去做臥底接近龍四的女兒龍曉暉（簡慧真飾）。宋子豪為了弟弟的安全，不得不假釋出獄，協助警方調查..<br />\n<br />\n3.砵仔糕（周潤發飾）、阿占（張國榮飾）和紅豆（鍾楚紅飾）均是孤兒，在養父（曾江飾）栽培下成為國際大盜。長大後成了幫他賺錢的藝術品大盜，而三人同時又認了警察（朱江飾）為乾爹。<br />\n<br />\n法國巴黎博物館內，名畫《赫林之女僕》被人盜走。與此同時，阿海、阿占和紅豆三人以敏捷身手盜得另一幅名畫，在與法國大哥交易時得知名畫《赫林之女僕》在妖氣重重的古堡內，他們在曾江安排下成功地盜取此畫之後，反被集團原兇曾江與法國大哥合謀設下陷阱，派人追殺滅口。阿海駕車與殺手快艇相撞&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n7 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9c6be0ece0bc8ec9bd89ca19704b5730530686","tid":182470,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:31:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b628f4d3fd9a9cd8b4dc7df1aeaa44d6541be69","tid":182470,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T11:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70866a207c4384aacfa0ab4cc322e960a543258","tid":182470,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T12:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1c0c3f589bc74460486b6881ddf2c34dc37d35","tid":182470,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T12:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236240764a2e128e92e7e1bc0937cbe8aab6d13a","tid":182470,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af56ed63309ed3540b9dd8868308ea78b8741c4","tid":182470,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T14:05:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f